cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving the performance of neural machine translation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes methods for optimizing the performance of the neural network, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the optimal stopping criteria for these methods, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of beam search in image captioning, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
